<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <style>
        /* 1. Body (Global layout, background image, and text color) */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: white; /* Changed text color to white */
            padding: 20px;
            /* Added background image and styling */
            background-image: url('Birddy.webp'); 
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        /* 2. Main Heading */
        h1 {
            color: #ffffff; /* Changed to white for visibility */
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffffff; 
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* 3. Subheadings */
        h2 {
            color: #00e676; /* Changed to a bright color for visibility */
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        /* 4. Paragraphs */
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #f0f0f0; /* Light gray for readability */
        }

        /* 5. Unordered Lists */
        ul {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); /* Semi-transparent background to read text */
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        /* Class 1: Custom layout container for photos */
        .photo-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        /* Class 2: Style to control and resize the images properly */
        .profile-photo {
            width: 300px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        /* Class 3: Highlight effect for specific list items */
        .favorite-highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff5252; /* Lighter red for contrast */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>About Me Danny!!</h1>

    <!-- Facts About Yourself -->
    <h2>Facts About Me</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>I have a cat named Spotty.</li>
        <li>I used to be fat and chubby boy, I am obviously the brown one!!!</li>
        <li>I like hiking.</li>
        <li>I went to a Catholic School growing up.</li>
    </ul>

    <img src="fatty.jpeg" alt="Image not found" width="500px" height="200"/>
    <img src="Spotty.jpeg" alt="Image not found" width="200px" height="200"/>

</body>
</html>

